arg.description:
method used to timestamp measurements; possible values: {
    TIME_FROM_INTERNAL_OSC,
    TIME_FROM_SYNC_PULSE_IN,
    TIME_FROM_PTP_1588,
    TIME_FROM_ROS_TIME
    }

point type for the generated point cloud;
   available options: {
    original,
    native,
    xyz,
    xyzi,
    xyzir
    }
